<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:57:29 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>荷兰路由器已发货</title><link>https://some.pics/69e9363640d16</link><description>&lt;p&gt;荷兰路由器正在被拾取 :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="NL routers are being picked up :)" height="2868" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chilli/69e9363640d16.png" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chilli.some.pics"&gt;@chilli&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:57:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>1994年印第安人球场旧照</title><link>https://some.pics/69e9348d260df</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天又扫描了几张底片。这是我的朋友凯文和我在雅各布斯球场（现进步球场）的合影。这张照片拍摄于1994年4月15日至17日的某个周末，当时克利夫兰印第安人队主场迎战堪萨斯城皇家队，进行三场系列赛。印第安人队输了，但我们依然玩得很开心。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two men posing together in  the stands at Jacobs Field. The man on the left wears glasses and a red and blue retro-style Cleveland Indians jersey, while the man on the right wears glasses and a denim jacket. The man on the right is holding up a white container above their heads. Both are smiling at the camera." height="4920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69e9348d260df.jpg" width="3280"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:50:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>光影交错</title><link>https://some.pics/69e91b1993830</link><description>&lt;p&gt;投下阴影。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A gardening device and blackberry branches leaving strong shadows on a white wall." height="4494" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69e91b1993830.jpg" width="2529"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 19:01:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>365个瞬间之一</title><link>https://some.pics/69e87189408ef</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今年#365moments中的一个瞬间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A tricolour Jack Russell Terrier is lying on his belly between a pink blanket and a yellow pillow looking straight into the camera, but is about to fall asleep. His ears lying flat on both sides. " height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69e87189408ef.jpg" width="3096"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 06:58:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>大事发生！</title><link>https://some.pics/69e83fd556675</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它正在发生！😮&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Nintendo Switch 2 sitting on a gray couch cushion with a Switch OLED sitting next to it (vertically), in the process of transferring data " height="2781" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/69e83fd556675.jpg" width="3128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 03:26:28 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>